snippet: London’s police chief said Tuesday that the cost of keeping watch on Mr. Assange, who is holed up in the Ecuadorean Embassy there, was draining resources and must be reviewed.
lead_paragraph: London’s police chief said Tuesday that the cost of keeping watch on Mr. Assange, who is holed up in the Ecuadorean Embassy there, was draining resources and must be reviewed.

headline.main: Britain: Julian Assange Duty Is Draining Police Coffers, London Chief Says
